{"tid":1639740,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"壞交通燈 = 消耗一隊防暴","createTime":"2019-10-08T16:58:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-09T01:57:02.000Z","uid":276527,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"9fc157e3a66c9078229d3f0c8404701991338e9c","tid":1639740,"uid":276527,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T16:58:14.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://twitter.com/HongKongFP/status/1181518868868517888?s=20\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FHongKongFP%2Fstatus%2F1181518868868517888%3Fs%3D20&d=cH2nQL%2B7gNVGRZzFZPB6VgqYqcROYCvJBJmaWwU8HGA%3D&h=ab96247a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FHongKongFP%2Fstatus%2F1181518868868517888%3Fs%3D20&h=66ba8960\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/HongKongFP/status/1181518868868517888?s=20</a><br />\n<br />\n畫面起碼5個green object + 2衝<br />\n<br />\n利申: 我係駕駛者, 無燈未驚過, 最多開慢d"},{"pid":"4c90486dcf2ec56adf13142514bcc7be7244dbd1","tid":1639740,"uid":312125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T16:58:42.000Z","msg":"（分析+行動）政府有意部署封網，封網後香港變新疆！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1639585\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1639585</a><br />\n<br />\n星期二（10月8日）早上，港鐵就宣布提前在晚上八點停駛，點解政府未卜先知出現動亂？其實政府有心製造一個長期嘅亂局，然後用緊急法立更多惡法，其中最近葉國謙就話要準備封網，呢樣嘢可以對香港抗爭造成極嚴重打擊。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: gold;\"><ins>斷網可毒啞香港人，新疆前車可鑑</ins></span></strong><br />\n斷網真係落實嘅話，<span style=\"color: red;\">最惡劣係好似新疆咁徹底斷網</span>，只有政府部門先可以上網，<span style=\"color: red;\">徹底封網的話，大家不但難以互通抗爭消息，而且香港訊息難以傳到海外，香港人也難以接收海外消息。西方人對香港嘅了解，只能經過政府嘅官方說法，或極少數流出嘅真相。</span><span style=\"color: gold;\">新疆早在2009年封網，同時限制境外人士到新疆旅遊，斷絕新疆對外聯繫，結果近年就出現新疆集中營。呢方面大家一定要警惕！</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>大家不能掉以輕心</strong><br />\n或者有人認為政府會顧及香港嘅國際環境唔會輕易斷網，但現在中共已經失去理性，當中央黔驢技窮，損害香港利益而徹底封網並非不可。就好似半年前大家都唸唔到香港已經失去遊行以及戴口罩嘅自由。<br />\n<br />\n本文為節錄，全文請到此瀏覽：<br />\n<br />\n（分析+行動）政府有意部署封網，封網後香港變新疆！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1639585\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1639585</a>"},{"pid":"1d097cd4d9726509f533188d17895db90554dbc8","tid":1639740,"uid":276527,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T16:58:56.000Z","msg":"P牌推唔到 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a97925cac688726ce9437ff77c8dd15bc3e98f2","tid":1639740,"uid":262899,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T16:59:03.000Z","msg":"幫你推～<br />\n<br />\n幫手推一推～ 感謝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n被捕求助（對唔住手足）<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1633560\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1633560</a>"},{"pid":"0bff4e8a92337d9b358fc51ea6086a61cccc5eba","tid":1639740,"uid":71428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T01:16:11.000Z","msg":"唔拆交通燈呀<br />\n黑裝修 紅裝飾 藍罷買 黃幫襯"},{"pid":"141ad531706649407138e4aaa9a649c30809ced7","tid":1639740,"uid":158613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9fc157e3a66c9078229d3f0c8404701991338e9c","tid":1639740,"uid":276527,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T16:58:14.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://twitter.com/HongKongFP/status/1181518868868517888?s=20\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FHongKongFP%2Fstatus%2F1181518868868517888%3Fs%3D20&d=cH2nQL%2B7gNVGRZzFZPB6VgqYqcROYCvJBJmaWwU8HGA%3D&h=ab96247a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FHongKongFP%2Fstatus%2F1181518868868517888%3Fs%3D20&h=66ba8960\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/HongKongFP/status/1181518868868517888?s=20</a><br />\n<br />\n畫面起碼5個green object + 2衝<br />\n<br />\n利申: 我係駕駛者, 無燈未驚過, 最多開慢d"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T01:57:02.000Z","msg":"特登唔整 扮撚曬野<br />\n之前次次最多2日就搞返掂曬<br />\n仲有呀，整燈都唔係班黑狗整啦<br />\n出黎攞彩指揮交通<br />\n你含